{"tid":2182660,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陶輝妻涉恐嚇《蘋果》記者獲放生 私隱署：不涉刑事停止調查","createTime":"2020-08-31T12:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T13:05:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"38e84ab684f9f6f77023528fe1226253e5b7b49b","tid":2182660,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T12:37:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200831/QLYWDMT6TVHHPMXVRXTBYY4TAQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200831%2FQLYWDMT6TVHHPMXVRXTBYY4TAQ%2F&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr08g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=e0e985e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200831%2FQLYWDMT6TVHHPMXVRXTBYY4TAQ%2F&h=2626afbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200831/QLYWDMT6TVHHPMXVRXTBYY4TAQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》早前踢爆警務處助理處長陶輝的警長妻子張雅詩涉無牌經營旅館，報道刊出後，張的Facebook個人賬戶頭像換成負責該報道的小組組長近照，涉事記者其後向私隱專員公署投訴，公署今日（31日）回覆指，認為事件不涉刑事行為，亦沒有披露記者的私人生活，決定停止調查。有學者批評公署以「最低標準，輕輕放過」，並不符公眾期望，破壞記者在受保障下繼續監察權貴的安全基礎，「意味相當令人不安，不符公眾利益。」"},{"pid":"050f0658ba9a65cacf168e7a4e8534b7349ad736","tid":2182660,"uid":354682,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T12:38:46.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95acff449b5116cc4b8a16c21b4af6ad9501f14","tid":2182660,"uid":305602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T12:39:35.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2dt0hDKK130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2dt0hDKK130&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2s